snippet.title: Fears to Fathom : Woodbury Getaway - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In the fifth episode of Fears to Fathom you play as Sydney Harper, a 23-year-old working at a consulting firm plans a weekend getaway to a rental in Woodbury with her college friends. Little did they know what was about to unfold during their stay. Sydney survived as she made the right choices.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2961530/Fears_to_Fathom__Woodbury_Getaway/

Fears to Fathom - Woodbury Getaway releases on 12th September 2024.

Twitter :  https://x.com/theRayll?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor
